title: Howard Stern Presents Prophets Of Rage
description:
Howard Stern Presents: Prophets Of Rage  (23:55)

The supergroup featuring members of Rage Against The Machine, Cypress Hill and Public Enemy give Howard 101 a live concert from the Hollywood Palladium. Plus, exclusive interviews with the band.

* "Prophets Of Rage".
* Forming The Band.
* "Sleep Now In The Fire".
* Rage Against The Machine songs.
* "Bulls On Parade".
* The Live Stage Shows.
* "Killing In The Name"
